### Inventory Service API Test File

### Create inventory item
POST http://localhost:8083/api/inventory
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productCode": "PROD-001",
  "productName": "Laptop",
  "quantity": 100,
  "price": 999.99,
  "reorderLevel": 10
}

### Get all inventory
GET http://localhost:8083/api/inventory

### Get inventory by product code
GET http://localhost:8083/api/inventory/product/PROD-001

### Reserve stock
POST http://localhost:8083/api/inventory/reserve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productCode": "PROD-001",
  "quantity": 5,
  "orderId": 1
}

### Confirm reservation
POST http://localhost:8083/api/inventory/confirm?productCode=PROD-001&quantity=5

### Release reservation
POST http://localhost:8083/api/inventory/release?productCode=PROD-001&quantity=5

### Update stock
PUT http://localhost:8083/api/inventory/product/PROD-001/stock?quantity=150

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8083/actuator/health
